### 결제 요청 - 정상 (201 Created, PENDING + transactionKey)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### 결제 요청 - 회원 인증 헤더 누락 (401 Unauthorized)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### 결제 요청 - 대상 주문 미존재/타인 소유 (404 Not Found)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "orderId": 99999,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### 결제 요청 - 이미 결제 존재 (409 Conflict)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678-9012-3456"
}

### 결제 요청 - 카드 번호 형식 오류 (400 Bad Request)
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/payments
Content-Type: application/json
X-Loopers-LoginId: testuser
X-Loopers-LoginPw: Kyle!2030

{
  "orderId": 1,
  "cardType": "SAMSUNG",
  "cardNo": "1234-5678"
}
